{"tid":2300112,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"肌膚亮到發光！IU寫真照「背部全裸」正面深V設計網暴動","createTime":"2020-11-25T09:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T18:01:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc3da5273c79a816649dfc909650b7cca927b6a","tid":2300112,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"有「國民妹妹」之稱的IU李知恩，年僅27歲的她在戲劇、歌壇甚至是綜藝節目都有亮眼表現，最近她在IG上公佈將推出寫真年曆「2021 SEASON GREETING」，首張形象照也出爐，穿上超美夢幻多層次網紗禮服，優雅的倒臥在粉色沙發上，纖細白嫩的手臂在燈光下簡直「瞬間散發女神光！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/25/2901590-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F25%2F2901590-PH.jpg&h=4deb2088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓星IU先前曬出工作花絮照。（圖／翻攝自 dlwlrma IG）<br />\n<br />\n最近IU的IG上都是滿滿的拍照花絮，而且禮服一件比一件還要美，先前才曝光全白平口低胸洋裝、以及大紅色多層次禮服，露出IU的超級纖細手臂與完美鎖骨，已經讓粉絲迫不及待想要看完成品，而IU也非常寵粉，已經釋出了第一張時尚年曆照片，網友狂讚：「根本美翻！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/25/2901589-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F25%2F2901589-PH.jpg&h=ad035262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓星IU年曆寫真照片首度曝光。（圖／翻攝自 dlwlrma IG）<br />\n<br />\n另外，IU也入選本年度最受歡迎韓星第三名，僅次第一名的劉在錫、以及第二名的BTS防彈少年團，IU李知恩總在今年推出數位單曲〈Eight〉以及投入到電影《Dream》的拍攝，表現十分亮眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/25/2901586-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F25%2F2901586-PH.jpg&h=3efba6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲韓星IU曬出無濾鏡高顏值工作照。（圖／翻攝自 dlwlrma IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/25/2901587-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F25%2F2901587-PH.jpg&h=ff757964&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46b67b61aa67642e1e9caf58afee4cabdf45961b","tid":2300112,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:06:36